headline: Cloudflare Zaraz launches new privacy features in response to French CNIL standards
keywords: Zaraz, Privacy, Google Analytics, CNIL, France, Product News
description: Last week, the French National Data Protection Authority, CNIL, published guidelines for a GDPR-compliant way of loading Google Analytics. Today, Zaraz is launching a new set of features to help our customers use Google Analytics and similar tools, while meeting those strict standards
